text: Terrence Leonard Tisdell (born 16 March 1998) is a Liberian footballer who plays as a winger for Israeli club Hapoel Petah Tikva and the Liberia national team. ==Club career== Born in Monrovia, Tisdell has played for FC Fassell, LISCR and Costa do Sol. He joined Portuguese club Sanjoanense in August 2018. He returned to Africa in July 2019, signing with South African side Baroka.
